tool_description: An API that lists the Naruto clan and its member's details. Currently, the database is under development. I will add some more details asap.
name: Naruto Database
title: Naruto Database

api_list.name: Aburame
api_list.description: Lists all the members of clan Aburame!
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://naruto-database.p.rapidapi.com/clan?name=aburame"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "naruto-database.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
